snippet.textDisplay: love you jennna , you’re a kind of person I really look up to and share SO MANY VIEWS TRAITS WEIRDNESS AND OPINIONS and VALUES WITH, if be honored to get to know ALL of you guys as friends and hopefully someday that’s possible, Ive been through a lot in my life and one thing I’ve always had to look forward to is your videos and I’m NEVER disappointed, you’re a wonderful person just doing you and making the world a better place by just being, you are my spirit animal😂I hope that’s not weird lol, I’ve literally just been a fan since I was in fifth grade and I’m in college now and have never missed a video😂you’re one of my favorite people and I know we don’t actually know you like you guys have personal lives and everything so obviously I’m speaking from what you allow us to be apart of but I’m grateful that you do share your life. Julien is absolutely hilarious And I’m happy you two share a similar since of humor and work so well together, you’re so similar yet different at the same time, there’s a reason you two are otters and I see it and I’m so happy for you guys. The way you both love your dogs aka your little babies is so amazing, it kind of reminds me of my aunt and that makes me smile. Dogs are people too and members of the family man, but I feel like you guys go beyond that sometimes in your own way and I think that’s awesome and admirable. You inspire people to be better and open up minds. You’re truly good people so don’t doubt yourself and keep it up!!
